Definition: a state of being relaxed and feeling no pain
Example: he is a man who enjoys his comfort; she longed for the comfortableness of her armchair
Synonyms: verb, body, discomfort, comfortableness, adj, all, comfortable, condition, a, state, of, being, relaxed, and, feeling, no, pain, he, is, man, who, enjoys, his, she, longed, for, the, her, armchair
Category: noun.state
